		<BaseHead title="LeShea Signature" description="The premium personal and executive brand of DeAndra L. Flowers." />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>LeShea Signature</h1>
			<p>
				LeShea Signature is the premium personal and executive brand of DeAndra L. Flowers, created for refined leadership, transformational teaching, signature experiences, and purpose-driven influence.
			</p>
			<p>
				This space will feature speaking, workshops, leadership resources, curated experiences, and signature offerings.
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
